    "id": "306aec94-4d3c-8008-9985-d94ba1780069",
    "title": "Top Note",
    "name": "Top Note",
    "subtitle": "A widget based iOS app",
    "summary": "Top Note is a focused productivity app for people who tend to ignore reminders or feel weighed down by long to-do lists. It takes a simpler approach: one reminder, flashcard, or note at a time. You can complete it or skip it, and if you skip, it returns sooner through a spaced repetition system that keeps important things visible.\n\n\nThis design encourages accountability and steady progress. It helps build habits, strengthen memory, and keep personal ideas within reach—without the noise of endless lists.\n\n\nWhy it works\nTop Note combines two familiar ideas: single-task focus and spaced repetition. Together they keep your attention on what matters next, reinforcing memory and consistency over time.\n\n\nFeatures\n– One-at-a-time reminders that reduce distraction.\n– Skip and repeat so skipped items return sooner.\n– Spaced repetition flashcards for better recall.\n– Widget-first design that keeps the app close at hand.\n– Flexible note support for quotes, goals, or brief thoughts.\n– Simple setup inside the app; most use happens in the widget.\n\n\nBest for\n– People who often dismiss reminders.\n– Habit tracking and reinforcement.\n– Short study or review sessions.\n– Keeping a meaningful note visible through the day.\n\n\nTop Note makes productivity manageable by narrowing your focus. Instead of managing a list, you engage with one small task—and let time handle the rest.",
